          "tz": 480
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Liang Zhen",
          "email": "liang@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2013-01-01 08:23:09.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-2432 ptlrpc: alloc_rqbd spin on vmap_area_lock",
        "message": "LU-2432 ptlrpc: alloc_rqbd spin on vmap_area_lock\n\nvmalloc based allocations can potentially take a very long time to\ncomplete due to a regression in the kernel. As a result, MDS service\nthreads might lock up for certain periods of time while all of the\ncores spin on the vmap_area_lock down in ptlrpc_alloc_rqbd.\n\nTihs patch only allow one thread of each CPT to enter rqbd\nalloation path.\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I4ba442801859ae58cf8e8dd8ae18af1062379639\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
